snippet.title: ♾️The official trailer for Version 1.4 [Revelry Season] is now live!
snippet.description:
♾️The official trailer for Version 1.4 [Revelry Season] is now live!
Behind every mask lies a wilder fantasy. Under the spotlight, wishes burn brighter than the sun!
Dance! Let the rhythm of joy guide your feet~
Step onto the world's stage and witness this fantastic party—

Infinity Nikki Version 1.4 [Revelry Season] begins on March 25th (UTC-7)!
Get ready for:
✨ New event gameplay
✨ New Realm Challenge
✨ Free outfit updates in [Store: Heartfelt Gifts]
...and so much more! Stylists, don't miss out on the excitement—dive in and explore!
